WEBVTT

00:00:58.946 --> 00:01:01.336
because I was the only
Jewish kid in class.

00:01:01.910 --> 00:01:04.283
So I couldn't wait to get
started to work on this,

00:01:04.307 --> 00:01:06.917
so I could introduce Kevin to my robot.

00:01:06.941 --> 00:01:07.971
(Laughter)

00:01:07.995 --> 00:01:12.238
(Robot noises)

00:01:17.552 --> 00:01:18.944
(Laughter)

00:01:18.968 --> 00:01:22.817
But that wasn't the kind of robot
my dad had in mind.

00:01:22.841 --> 00:01:23.909
(Laughter)

00:01:23.933 --> 00:01:27.565
See, he owned a chromium-plating company,

00:01:27.589 --> 00:01:33.462
and they had to move heavy steel parts
between tanks of chemicals.